  "prompt": "Which is currently the most affordable city in South Korea (in terms of rent)?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, the most affordable city in South Korea in terms of rent is typically smaller cities and towns rather than the major metropolitan areas like Seoul, Busan, or Incheon. Cities such as Daegu, Daejeon, and Gwangju generally have lower rental costs compared to Seoul. However, for the most current and detailed information, it is recommended to check local real estate listings or consult with expats living in various South Korean cities. Prices can fluctuate, and specific areas within a city can vary greatly in affordability.",
